{"tid":1084972,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"毁滅之刃，血鬼術討論","createTime":"2019-03-30T19:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T16:23:27.000Z","uid":123737,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78766036f30ddbd280e6c73b7266f6b78552212e","tid":1084972,"uid":123737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T19:36:49.000Z","msg":"頭先返睇緊，忽然間覺得鬼嘅能力應該係建基於自己嘅慾望/擅長嘅事物。<br />\n舉下例子:<br />\n<br />\n下五：其實想要返同屋企人嘅聯繫，所以能力就演變左係蜘蛛絲，想補償番同屋企人冇咗嘅聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n上六:兄妹唔想分開所以可以合體。阿哥擅長用鐮刀，所以能力關於鐮刀。<br />\n<br />\n上五：因為覺得金魚好有藝術氣息所以自己有魚嘅部份。<br />\n<br />\n上四:怕事，所以自己可以產生分身去幫佢做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n上二:應該想越來越強所以能力都關自己本身嘅武術事。<br />\n<br />\n無慘:唔想死所以斬頸都唔死<br />\n<br />\n純粹廢up，對於討論劇情冇咩幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddd2b46358319c8857ec3987d2a7d20fa9b2faa","tid":1084972,"uid":211537,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T19:48:31.000Z","msg":"鬼滅之刃喎大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b633819e8208efdd157fceec8b257774e4fb0f47","tid":1084972,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:20:09.000Z","msg":"新上六: 為人陰濕,所以血鬼術都係陰陰濕濕"},{"pid":"26a3b25f0df15c2003bdc01c284add9f2b28209e","tid":1084972,"uid":123737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ddd2b46358319c8857ec3987d2a7d20fa9b2faa","tid":1084972,"uid":211537,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T19:48:31.000Z","msg":"鬼滅之刃喎大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"眼訓到自己打錯字都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba40e54439087f1928b4604e69a39201ba794726","tid":1084972,"uid":123737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b633819e8208efdd157fceec8b257774e4fb0f47","tid":1084972,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:20:09.000Z","msg":"新上六: 為人陰濕,所以血鬼術都係陰陰濕濕"},"c